 New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt;">8.4.</span><span style="width: 16.95pt; text-indent: 0pt; display: inline-block;"></span><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt; text-decoration: underline;">Release</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt;">. To the fullest extent permitted by applicable law, Buyer releases the </span><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt;">Usechain</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt; text-decoration: underline;"></span><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt;">Parties from responsibility, liability, claims, demands, and/or Damages (actual and consequential) of every kind and nature, known and unknown (including, but not limited to, claims of negligence), arising out of or related to disputes between Buyer and the acts or omissions of third parties.</span></p><p style="line-height: 12.25pt; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt;">8.5.</span><span style="width: 17pt; text-indent: 0pt; display: inline-block;"></span><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt; text-decoration: underline;">Indemnification</span><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt;">.</span></p><p style="line-height: 12.65pt; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span></p><ol type="a" style="margin: 0pt; padding-left: 0pt;"><li style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 49.33pt; padding-left: 4.67pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt;">To the fullest extent permitted by applicable law, Buyer will indemnify, defend and h